beer.beer_description:

Expect a lip puckering sour punch on a decedent creamy body, carried with a balanced fruit, and caramel malt sweetness.

items.checkin_comment: This is tartier than a motel room full of barrio whores, mouthing their invitation to treat to the anxious john with their cerise-coloured lips. Cherries for sure & the negroni colour is inviting but I don’t get any pastry or creaminess. Not for me.
